name: Surkhab Chia Seeds(300g) – High In Fiber, Protein & Aid In Weight Loss -Maxican Seeds
description: Chia seeds,  are small black or white seeds that come from the plant Salvia hispanica. They are packed with nutrients, including fiber, protein, omega-3 fatty acids, and various vitamins and minerals. Chia seeds are known for their ability to absorb liquid and form a gel-like consistency, making them a popular ingredient in puddings, smoothies, and baked goods. They are also used as a topping for yogurt or cereal. Chia seeds are considered a superfood and are believed to have several health benefits, such as aiding in digestion, promoting heart health, and providing sustained energy.

name: Surkhab Desi Gur 100% Pure Jaggery - No Artificial Color -500 Gram
description: Jaggery, known as "Gurr" in Urdu, is a type of unrefined sugar made from sugarcane or date palm sap. It is brown in color and has a rich, caramel-like flavor. Jaggery is often used as a natural sweetener in various dishes and desserts. It is considered healthier than refined sugar because it retains some of the minerals and nutrients present in the sugarcane juice. Jaggery is also believed to have medicinal properties and is used in traditional Ayurvedic medicine for its potential health benefits.

name: Surkhab Organic Olive Leaf Tea

name: Surkhab Roasted Flaxseeds - Flex Seed
description: Flax seeds, known as "alsi ke beej" in Urdu, are small seeds that come from the flax plant. They are a rich source of omega-3 fatty acids, fiber, and various essential nutrients. name: Surkhab Pink Salt 100% Pure & Finest Quality
description: Pink salt, also known as Himalayan salt, is a type of rock salt that is mined in the Himalayan region. It gets its pink color from the minerals present in the salt, such as iron.
